biography:

2002-2008: academic studies Physics and Computer Engineering at the University of Osnabrück, Germany.
2008-2013: PhD studies in the NanoScience research group of Prof. Michael Reichling at the University of Osnabrück.
since 2013: Sensor Developer at ROSEN in Lingen, Germany.
